{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Polish quota was about 4,000, and there were many more Polish Jews under the Polish quota than the German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So this is-- this is why it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So then, when finally [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- in-- when Israel was established, I was out of Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that's when many were able to go to Israel, finally, and particularly, they had that fell under this quota law.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But being under German quota was-- was-- was a break, because Truman signed into law at that time that they could use two or three more years where there were no immigrants and add them up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So instead of 14,000, they were allowed 42,000 Jews for the German quota, for instance, or in Poland, instead of 4,000, 12,000.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So some-- some of us could go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many of the ones for the German quota could go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When did you find out, or how did you find out, about what happened in Germany and [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The concentration-- well, after the war, the stories came through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Family of mine, a lot of families, a lot of my-- my mother's family-- I mean, on my mother's side, as well from my father's side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many, many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a cousin of my father who did come back, who wrote the first letter how conditions were in Germany from 1946.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have that letter, but it's written in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I published it in the paper in Shanghai, because it was the first, actually, report mainly about Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew that she survived because she contacted us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her husband got killed-- first husband got killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her brother got killed, who was very close with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That she could tell that to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
